array.item:
Renting a car occurs in several stages:

            1. You choose the car you like;
            2. Familiarize yourself with the terms of car rental on the website, or consult with
            manager by phone or messenger;
            3. Send the documents for verification by the security service. This stage takes no more
            20 minutes;
            4. The manager confirms the reservation with a reply message.

            At the appointed date and time we meet with you to sign the contract and transfer
            selected car. The conclusion of a contract is possible only if the client has
            Passport and driver\'s license in hand.
